{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Shopify 2.0 section named "Responsive Image Slider" using Swiper.js.  
    
    Requirements:
    - Fully responsive for desktop & mobile.  
    - Each slide allows:
      - Desktop image
      - Mobile image
      - Optional heading, subheading, button (with link).  
    - Admin can dynamically add unlimited slides (3, 4, 5, etc.) using blocks.  
    - Settings to enable/disable autoplay, arrows, and dots.  
    - Custom styling: text color, button color, text alignment.  
    - Images must lazy-load.  
    - Slides reorderable from the theme editor.  
    - Optimize for fast load (minified CSS/JS, use Swiper CDN).  
    - Compatible with Shopify Sense theme.  
    
    Dynamic Sizing (Desktop & Mobile):  
    - Section settings must allow **separate width and height controls for desktop and mobile**.  
    - Width options: Full width (100%), Custom width in px/%, Container width.  
    - Height options: Full screen (100vh), Fixed height (px), or Auto.  
    - Admin can set different values for desktop and mobile (e.g. 100vh desktop, 500px mobile).  
    - Width and height values must be applied using CSS variables and responsive media queries.

{% enddoc %}
